                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Swamp striders\u2019 fur supports thriving colonies of algae that emit malodorous, flammable gas. Creatures in the algal gas effect are sickened while they remain in the aura and for 1 round afterward (Fortitude DC 11 negates). Creatures with active environmental protections or no sense of smell are immune to this sickened effect.",
