            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "When a swamp strider takes fire damage, it also gains the burning (1d8 F) condition, after which the creature\u2019s algal gas and flammable abilities are disabled for 1 hour. While it burns, the swamp strider\u2019s attacks deal an additional 1d4 fire damage.",
